name: Natural Log Skateboards - Roots Mid 24" Cruiser
description: WIth its inspiration from the roots, the Roots Mini will take you back to the first days of skateboarding. The shape and the boards bamboo/fibre-cloth hybrid construction gives it all the performance characteristics of a contemporary skateboard. Construction Handcrafted: Each board is made one at a time, from start to finish. Eco Friendly Log strive to only use high quality, sustainable materials. Bamboo is the primary wood choice due to it's strength and performance, while being a renewable resource. All of the boards are laminated using Entropy Resins' Super Sap, a bio based glue system that adds spring and pop. Performance 3 ply bamboo construction ensure a lively pop and strength. 2 internal layers of tri-axial fibre cloth allows for a thinner, lighter and stronger deck while still maintaining a responsive flex. Set Up Ace 00 Trucks OJ HotJuice 60 mm Wheels Mini Logo bearings. Khiro soft riser pads. Clear grip-tape (If choosing a full set up, please select wheel colour and grip-tape in the notes at the checkout.) Dimensions 24 Long 7 Wide 4.5 Tail 14 Wheelbase Please note that each board is made to order in San Diego and will take 3 - 5 days to complete plus an estimated 3 days shipping within the US and an estimated 7 - 14 days outside of the US. See the full range here.

name: Natural Log Skateboards - Roots 29" Cruiser
description: The Roots model is designed as a versatile classic cruiser. The board features a wide nose, and is shaped to have a hint of flex for a smoother ride that takes you back to the roots. Construction Handcrafted: Each board is made one at a time, from start to finish. Eco Friendly Log strive to only use high quality, sustainable materials. Bamboo is the primary wood choice due to it's strength and performance, while being a renewable resource. All of the boards are laminated using Entropy Resins' Super Sap, a bio based glue system that adds spring and pop. Performance 3 ply bamboo construction ensure a lively pop and strength. 2 internal layers of tri-axial fibre cloth allows for a thinner, lighter and stronger deck while still maintaining a responsive flex. Set Up 159 mm Independent trucks. OJ 60mm HotJuice Wheels Mini Logo bearings. Khiro soft riser pads. Clear grip-tape (If choosing a full set up, please select wheel colour and grip-tape in the notes at the checkout.) Dimensions 29 Long 9 Wide 6.5 Tail 16 Wheelbase Please note that each board is made to order in San Diego and will take 3 - 5 days to complete plus an estimated 3 days shipping within the US and an estimated 7 - 14 days outside of the US. See the full range here.

name: Natural Log Skateboards - Rhythm 30" Cruiser
description: The Rhythm model is designed as an all around free ride board perfect for carving, cruising, and commuting. The board features a wide shape, long wheelbase, and a responsive flex crafted in a compact size. Construction Handcrafted: Each board is made one at a time, from start to finish. Eco Friendly Log strive to only use high quality, sustainable materials. Bamboo is the primary wood choice due to it's strength and performance, while being a renewable resource. All of the boards are laminated using Entropy Resins' Super Sap, a bio based glue system that adds spring and pop. Performance 3 ply bamboo construction ensure a lively pop and strength. 2 internal layers of tri-axial fibre cloth allows for a thinner, lighter and stronger deck while still maintaining a responsive flex. Set up Randall R2 150mm Trucks Seismic 68mm Cambria Wheels (3DM Brand) Mini Logo bearings. Khiro soft riser pads. Clear or Black grip-tape (If choosing a full set up, please select wheel colour and grip-tape in the notes at the checkout.) Dimensions 30 Long 9 Wide 3.5 Tail 21 Wheelbase Please note that each board is made to order in San Diego and will take 3 - 5 days to complete plus an estimated 3 days shipping within the US and an estimated 7 - 14 days outside of the US. See the full range here.

name: Bargain Tee
description:
You pick the size, we pick the tee.
You'll get one tee through the post from one of our labels.
We don't send misprints or damaged goods, only end of line, last few and last season items.
If there is anything that you don't wish to receive or you've had one from us before please let us know and we'll see what we can do.
